  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "chapterTitle": "纯属私事",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300055669_3_443-536",
          "range": "443-536",
          "rangeStart": 443,
          "rangeEnd": 536,
          "markText": "我有这样一种观念：在讲述任何事件之前，有必要告诉读者接下来是什么类型的文字。所以，现在我要告诉大家，下面讲述的不是什么重大事件，而只是在战争开始后的最初十五个月里发生在我身上的一些小事。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1759573006,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-10-04 18:16:46",
          "chapterUid": 3,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=443&rangeEnd=536",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=443&rangeEnd=536"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_3_5658-5688",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5658-5688",
      "markText": "经过慎重考虑，他们一致决定：不再考虑在我的住宅区内修建炮台。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5658&rangeEnd=5688",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5658&rangeEnd=5688"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_3_2260-2313",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2260-2313",
      "markText": "你所拥有的花园面积越大，你想要的也就会越多；你越是精心照料你的花园，花园里的一切越是会哭着喊着让你去照料。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2260&rangeEnd=2313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2260&rangeEnd=2313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_3_2101-2167",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2101-2167",
      "markText": "我准备在这里度过余生，准备就在自己卧室里那张崭新的床上悄然逝去。有时候，我会双手交叉，然后闭上双眼，想象自己死去时会是怎样一副尊容。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2101&rangeEnd=2167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2101&rangeEnd=2167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_6_1198-1283",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1198-1283",
      "markText": "在法国，你的厨师有一种秘而不宣的权利，那就是他在市场上买的任何东西，报价时都会多报5%，只要他没跟你多要一倍的钱，你就要谢天谢地，称赞他的善良和诚实，认定自己很是幸运了。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1198&rangeEnd=1283",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1198&rangeEnd=1283"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_3_4302-4358",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4302-4358",
      "markText": "我一直对穿制服的人有畏惧心理，所以，为了让自己感觉不那么拘谨，我已经在想象中扒掉了他们的制服，给他们换上了连衫裤",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300055669&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4302&rangeEnd=4358",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/47c32f80813ab7c3eg01965e?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4302&rangeEnd=4358"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300055669_12_1864-1902",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1864-1902",
      "markText": "要是这家伙真把自己淹死了反正我不在现场，而且我还警告过他，所以这事与我无关。",
